Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Dark Eyes Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And the Time Bomber card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In two turns, Sacrifice will be destroyed by Time Bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, your Monster as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no cards in my hand that can stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if there were, Pegasus read them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Pegasus' Millennium Eye will see it at the same time I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the Mind Scan,\N you can't do a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fusion of Light and Darkness:\N Black Chaos Descends"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Damn! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Answer us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You have something other than the cards to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Something else to believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Your other self isn't the only one with you in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not see them right away, but there should be others here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I understand, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Jounouchi! Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Do you guys remember the ring\N﻿of friendship we made before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Our hearts are with Yugi's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Even if we're separated, our hearts are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't care if it's "Power of Darkness" or whatever, nothing ﻿will break the bond of our friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi! We're all with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bond of our friendship will always be linked to your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm drawing a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Scan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless to try and stop me, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You cannot hide the identity of that card within the depths of your mind for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has entered Yugi boy's mind and is blocking me from entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't see the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There's just no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Indeed, he had a strong mind throughout the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's unthinkable for a player's mind to be capable of fending off the Power of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! Don't you even think about invading Yugi's mind again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus! Yugi won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonnna kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So get ready, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Guys, I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Unbelievable! To think your friends were capable ﻿of repelling me from the depths of your mind...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The power of your Millennium Eye is\N﻿not capable of tearing down the wall of our feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here I go, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Magic Card, Magic Box of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two boxes appeared on the field..?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have enough time to counter it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician escapes Sacrifice in time\N before Time Bomber self-destructs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Bomber has switched places and is now attached to Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Brain Control!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Brainwashing Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy can control \NSacrifice for one turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Have you completely forgotten\N﻿about the time bomb on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿By doing such a stupid thing, your Black Magician will be blown up by Time Bomber and you'll {\i1}lose{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I still have a set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The card left behind by my other soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ritual of Black Magic Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Ritual Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I sacrifice Time Bomber and Black Magician for the ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think he was going to use the time bomb for that purpose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Great Magician of Black Magic - Magician of Black Chaos, descends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Magician of Black Chaos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self left behind but one card when he was on the verge of collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Ritual of Black Magic Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The magician born from chaos, the\N﻿fusion of light and darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Controller of insanity!\N The master of all magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus! This is our trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Using this trump card, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never expected this of Yugi boy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this turn, Sacrifice will be freed from his brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On my next turn, Black Chaos will be absorbed by Sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I will gain all of its powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy! You cannot defeat me, even if you play to all your limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus, I have the bond\N with my friends in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Even the power of your\N Millennium Item can't break it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An unbreakable power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a card face-down on this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Also, I play another Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy has 2 set cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I can't see any of them due to his friends\N﻿blocking me from within his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What irritating bundlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The brainwashing effects on Sacrifice have worn ﻿off, and he becomes my Monster again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll use my trump card to teach you and your little comrades ﻿just how meaningless this "friendship" you speak of is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, I can just absorb Black Chaos using Sacrifice's Special Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure the same trick won't work twice on Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In that case, I'll play 2 cards on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll power up Sacrifice's Special Ability even further with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse Thousand Eyes Idol together with Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Evil God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Sacrifice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's got eyes covering its entire body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy, this Duel will signal the grand finale of the Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You will be cursed with a cruel defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}﻿Let our hearts blend with yours!\N Our bond of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you dare lose\N to Pegasus' Power of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, you can't give up!\N We're with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We won't know the result of this match until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the Special Ability of the Thousand Eyes Sacrifice I now have on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your Black Chaos\N will be unable to do a {\i1}thing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thousand Eyes Sacrifice's﻿ Special Ability...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The very moment my Thousand Eyes Sacrifice opens every eye on its body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the movement of every Monster on my opponent's field shall become sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}﻿Even though it's been fused, the enemy is still a Monster with 0 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll surely try to absorb Black Chaos and steal its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore to my other self!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.... let me draw one final card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A card that can defeat Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this card... to defeat... Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat you using Black Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No matter what tricks you pull, you\N﻿won't break the promise we made!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The final turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm counting on you, my Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Sacrifice's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Curse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And with this, your Monsters have all been paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Thousand Eyes Curse will remain on the field, holding its spell over your Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eternal curse...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In short, you will be trapped in\N﻿this everlasting curse forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All that remains now is for me to\N﻿activate the central Evil Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll suck in your Monster and steal its powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's over, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Evil Eye activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Magic Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the light from the Evil Eye hits Black Chaos, ﻿it'll be absorbed by Thousand Eyes Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You've made a grave miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating your Evil Eye also affected my set card, Kuriboh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Effect will now target him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wha-? When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In addition, I activated\N my other set card, Multiply!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh will be multiplied endlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! All the Kuribohs have been\N﻿affected by the Evil Eyes' light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice has no choice but to absorb every Kuriboh affected by the Evil Eyes' light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Sacrifice is trying to absorb the countless Kuriboh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was my aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kuriboh has the Special﻿ Ability to act like a living land mine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and self destruct\N on contact with the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Land mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿With Kuriboh's death, my Life Points\N﻿decrease by 300 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿However, all Thousand Eyes Sacrifice's\N﻿ thousands of eyes were destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy sacrificed Kuriboh just for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at this moment, Black Chaos is freed from its curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you prepared, Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Chaos, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spell of Destruction! Death Ultima!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Sacrifice ﻿was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We've... won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...lost...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, who holds the power\N of the Millennium Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, the {\b0}creator{\b1}\N of the game we played...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I lost...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Everyone gave their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Guys, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, I felt your pain while fighting-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt Yugi's pain while fighting and his joy of victory! I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Y-yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But I feel like we fought alongside you somehow, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Y-yeah, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿HEY! You jerks said\N everything I wanted to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿YUGI WON!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿ALL RIGHT!\N﻿ALL RIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's right! Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry and make him return your grandpa, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We'll make him keep his promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Where'd that guy go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oi, let's go look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But we can't just leave Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N﻿and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GUYS~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Did you return to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, I was on the floor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Do you really not remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That weird ring of yours took control of you again, Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Millennium Ring...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That ring...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah, it creeped me out, so I tossed it off the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thanks to Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I was saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}, can you watch over Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh... sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright. Let's go look for Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:19:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright! Yugi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But we have to hurry and find Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh? Pegasus was attacked by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can grandpa and the other's souls return to their bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We then find information about Pegasus'\N﻿past and how he got the Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿King of Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Duel standby!
